---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Section from "../components/ui/Section.astro";
---

<!-- Week 5 – SEO/OG meta: per-page title/description/ogType/ogImage -->
<!-- Edit these props if you want to change how the page appears in Google + social previews. -->

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms & Conditions | Facial Volume Harmony"
  description="Read the Terms & Conditions for using the Facial Volume Harmony website and purchasing our digital course, including payments, refunds, and content usage."
  ogType="website"
  ogImage="https://cdn.facialvolumeharmony.com/og-images/og_hero-poster.png"
>
  <Section title="Terms & Conditions">
    <div class="card">
      <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:28px;">1. Introduction</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;">
          These Terms and Conditions govern your use of the Facial Volume Harmony website (“we”, “us”, or “our”) and the purchase of our digital products.
          By using this website or purchasing our product, you agree to these Terms and Conditions.
        </p>

        <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:28px;">2. Product Description</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;">
          The product offered on this website is a digital course focused on natural facial care and supporting a harmonious appearance through gentle techniques.
        </p>

        <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px;">
          The course may include:
        </p>

        <ul style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;padding-left:20px;margin-top:10px;">
          <li>Tongue posture techniques</li>
          <li>Breathing techniques</li>
          <li>Gentle soft tissue work</li>
        </ul>

        <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px;">
          The goal is to support a more relaxed, open, and naturally balanced facial appearance.
        </p>

        <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px;">
          After purchase, you will receive access to digital content (such as videos and materials). No physical product will be shipped.
        </p>

        <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:28px;">3. Payments</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;">
          Payments are processed through a third-party payment provider. We do not store or have access to your payment details.
        </p>

        <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px;">
          Prices may be displayed in different currencies and may include applicable taxes depending on your location.
        </p>

        <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:28px;">4. Refund Policy</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;">
          Due to the digital nature of the product, all sales are final and non-refundable.
        </p>

        <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:28px;">5. Intellectual Property</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;">
          All content included in the course (including videos, text, graphics, and materials) is protected by intellectual property rights.
        </p>

        <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px;">
          By purchasing the course, you are granted a personal, non-transferable license to use the content.
          You may not copy, reproduce, distribute, or share the content with third parties without permission.
        </p>

        <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:28px;">6. Disclaimer</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;">
          The content of this course is provided for educational and informational purposes only.
        </p>

        <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px;">
          It is not medical advice and does not replace professional healthcare.
          You should consult a qualified professional before starting any techniques, especially if you have any medical conditions.
        </p>

        <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px;">
          Results may vary from person to person.
        </p>

        <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:28px;">7. Limitation of Liability</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;">
          We are not liable for any direct or indirect damages or outcomes resulting from the use of this product.
        </p>

        <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px;">
          Use of the content is at your own risk.
        </p>

        <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:28px;">8. Contact</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;">
          If you have any questions about these Terms and Conditions, you can contact us at:
        </p>

        <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px;">
          📧 hello@facialvolumeharmony.com
        </p>
    </div>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>